<h2 id="an-elegant-solution-for-deep-learning--plaidml">An elegant solution for Deep Learning â€” <a href="https://vertexai-plaidml.readthedocs-hosted.com/en/latest/installing.html">PlaidML</a></h2>

<p>Mainstream deep learning frameworks, such as Tensorflow, PyTorch, and Caffe 2, are not so friendly for AMD Mac.
Among the solutions introduced in Fabriceâ€™s blog, PlaidML is an elegant one to me.
The installation and configuration of PlaidML can be found in the documentation of <a href="https://vertexai-plaidml.readthedocs-hosted.com/en/latest/installing.html">PlaidML</a>.
The source code shown below is a quick guide for beginner, which is based on PlaidML + Keras:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
